    "description": "<p>You gain the following benefits for your Champion Class Features.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Master-at-Arms</span></strong></span></p><p>You learn 2 additional Maneuvers of your choice.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Fighting Spirit</span></strong></span></p><p>When you gain the benefits of Second Wind, you regain an additional 2 HP and 2 SP</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Adaptive Tactics</span></strong></span></p><p>Your Tactical Die is n<span style=\"color:rgba(44, 44, 43, 1);isolation:auto\" data-token-index=\"1\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\">ow a d10.</span></p>",
